metadata.name: leo davinci. portrait of a (II)
metadata.description: Messy Burst is a 100 piece collaboration between danctrl & ms_jif. A mind-bending exercise in visual art, fusing the hard edges of digital design with the wild, undulating strokes of digital airbrushed paint. These artworks are an electric shock to the eyes, a neon-colored meditation on the blurred lines between structure and chaos, order and anarchy.
